  "title": "R&D Assistant (Food Manufacturer) - SS10",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Job Tittle: R&D Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Hours: 0830am to 1730pm / 5 days</li><li>Salary: $2500 - $3000</li><li>location: Woodlands </li></ul><p><strong>Job scopes:</strong></p><p>1. To maintain and support the R&D department in seasoning compounding, new development and its application;</p><p>2. To support for monthly new seasoning or application method development and promotional item and their presentation;</p><p>3. To request for new raw materials or flavor sourcing for new product development to the Purchasing Dept;</p><p>4. To handle all new raw material registration, documentation and evaluation;</p><p>5. To perform QC such as sensory and visual checks on all finished products produced by the seasoning manufacturing line and incoming raw materials or new raw materials;</p><p>6. To evaluates current and alternative food ingredients.</p><p>7. To maintain the R&D laboratory and ensure cleanliness within the laboratory.</p><p>8. To carry out plant hygiene check.</p><p>9. To assist in the running and maintenance of HACCP and Halal quality system and its documentation.</p><p>10. Any other work as shall be assigned by the Company from time to time.</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma Food Science / Food Technology</li><li>At least 1 year experience in food seasoning</li></ul><p>Samuel Siaw</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd</p><p>EA No: 14C7279</p><p>Reg No: R2412474</p>",
